ZH: 他只是任由自己的感情控制着。
EN: He just lets his emotions control him.

ZH: 她任由别人的意见来决定自己的人生。
EN: She lets others' opinions determine her own life.

ZH: 我们不能任由自己的恐惧主宰我们的行动。
EN: We shouldn't allow our fears to dominate our actions.

ZH: 老板任由员工自由发挥创意。
EN: The boss allows employees to freely express their creativity.

ZH: 她任由自己的直觉来选择正确的答案。
EN: She lets her intuition guide her to the right answer.

ZH: 小孩子应该被任由做他们喜欢的事情。
EN: Children should be allowed to do what they enjoy.

ZH: 我不会任由别人的言论来影响我。
EN: I won't let others' comments affect me.

ZH: 任由这种情况继续下去是不可取的。
EN: It's not advisable to let this situation continue.

ZH: 老人们喜欢任由听音乐来放松心情。
EN: The elderly enjoy letting music relax their minds.

ZH: 我完全可以自己处理这个问题，不需要你任由干涉。
EN: I can handle this problem myself without letting you interfere.

ZH: 她明白她不能任由过去的错误来束缚自己的将来。
EN: She understands that she shouldn't let past mistakes constrain her future.

ZH: 他任由生活的压力让自己变得疲惫不堪。
EN: He lets the pressures of life exhaust him.

ZH: 我们不应该任由工作占据所有的时间。
EN: We shouldn't let work take up all our time.

ZH: 他们恋爱时完全任由心情来决定行动。
EN: When they are in love, they completely let their feelings dictate their actions.

ZH: 孩子们喜欢任由自己的想象力瞎编故事。
EN: Children enjoy letting their imagination run wild and making up stories.

ZH: 任由他自己选择未来的职业。
EN: Let him choose his own career path.

ZH: 她的父母不会任由她荒废学业。
EN: Her parents won't let her neglect her studies.

ZH: 他们任由天气决定是否要进行户外活动。
EN: They let the weather decide whether or not to engage in outdoor activities.

ZH: 我们应该任由时间来解决这个问题。
EN: We should let time resolve this issue.

ZH: 她从不任由失败打败自己。
EN: She never lets failure defeat her.

ZH: 他们必须任由自然界的规律运行。
EN: They must let the laws of nature run their course.
